OL,3,CPolice Scotland 'kicked out' staff for
OL,4,Cracism and sexism within the last year
OL,6,FIn an interview with ITV News, the
OL,7,Fchief constable said she cannot yet
OL,8,Fsay Police Scotland is no longer
OL,9,Fracist or sexist
OL,11,FPolice Scotland has "kicked out" staff
OL,12,Ffor racism and sexism within the last
OL,13,Fyear, the force's chief constable told
OL,14,FITV News.
OL,16,FWhen Jo Farrell took the job a year
OL,17,Fago, she inherited an organisation
OL,18,Fwhich her predecessor, Sir Iain
OL,19,FLivingstone, had just described as
OL,20,F"institutionally racist and sexist" in
OL,21,Fa high-profile media conference.
