OL,3,CPolice Scotland 'kicked out' staff for
OL,4,Cracism and sexism within the last year
OL,6,FToday, in an interview with ITV News,
OL,7,Fthe chief constable said she cannot
OL,8,Fyet say Police Scotland is no longer
OL,9,Fracist or sexist, but she revealed
OL,10,Fpeople have been sacked in her mission
OL,11,Fto detoxify the force.
OL,13,F"Some of these were part of criminal
OL,14,Fproceedings," she said. "Some were
OL,15,Fpart of internal disciplinary
OL,16,Fprocedures."
OL,18,FAnd she says she is still working to
OL,19,Fmake Police Scotland "anti-racist and
OL,20,Fanti-discriminatory."
