OL,3,CPolice Scotland 'kicked out' staff for
OL,4,Cracism and sexism within the last year
OL,6,FAsked when she thinks it will no
OL,7,Flonger be an institutionally racist
OL,8,Fand sexist police force, the chief
OL,9,Fconstable said she couldn't give a
OL,10,Ftime frame but insists it's her
OL,11,Fmission "every day."
OL,13,FAnother legacy inherited by Jo Farrell
OL,14,Fin her position as the head of Police
OL,15,FScotland is the investigation into the
OL,16,Ffunds and finances of the SNP.
OL,18,F'All of the investigation material has
OL,19,Fgone to the Crown Office,' Jo Farrell
OL,20,Fsays
