OL,3,CPolice Scotland 'kicked out' staff for
OL,4,Cracism and sexism within the last year
OL,6,FWhen pressed on whether her officers
OL,7,Fhave been overly cautious because of
OL,8,Fthe individuals involved, she refused
OL,9,Fto answer.
OL,11,FShe confirmed the case has now been
OL,12,Fhanded over to the Crown Office, which
OL,13,Fis the prosecuting authority in
OL,14,FScotland.
OL,16,FAlthough Police Scotland's chief
OL,17,Fconstable is still answering questions
OL,18,Fabout the past, today was supposed to
OL,19,Fbe a briefing on her vision for the
OL,20,Ffuture of the force.
