OL,3,CPolice Scotland 'kicked out' staff for
OL,4,Cracism and sexism within the last year
OL,6,FShe wants to see more police visible
OL,7,Fin Scottish communities.
OL,9,FThat means on foot, rather than in
OL,10,Fvehicles - a return to the old 'bobby
OL,11,Fon the beat' style to build trust and
OL,12,Fmake people feel safe.
OL,14,FTo be able to do this, the chief
OL,15,Fconstable wants her officers to spend
OL,16,Fless time with people having a mental
OL,17,Fhealth crisis - something, she says,
OL,18,Fis currently taking up far too much
OL,19,Fpolice time and resources.
