OL,3,CPolice Scotland 'kicked out' staff for
OL,4,Cracism and sexism within the last year
OL,6,F'I don't want officers sitting with
OL,7,Fpeople waiting for support for
OL,8,Felsewhere, that is not the core role
OL,9,Fof Police Scotland,' Jo Farrell says
OL,11,FThe chief constable would like
OL,12,Fcharities and the NHS to step in and
OL,13,Fhelp take some of this pressure off
OL,14,Fthe police.
OL,16,FBut it comes at a time of significant
OL,17,Fcuts to Scotland's mental health
OL,18,Fservices, with waiting lists already
OL,19,Fat record highs.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
