OL,3,CPolice Scotland 'kicked out' staff for
OL,4,Cracism and sexism within the last year
OL,6,FThe chief constable admits this could
OL,7,Fmean Police Scotland officers having
OL,8,Fto make difficult decisions to pull
OL,9,Fpeople away from dealing with someone
OL,10,Fwho is clearly in the midst of a
OL,11,Fmental health crisis, even if there's
OL,12,Fnobody else to fill the void.
OL,14,F"We would consider if there is a
OL,15,Fthreat to life," she said.
OL,17,FBut ultimately she admits there will
OL,18,Fbe dilemmas.
